column5: I know Shimano redesigned the sustain and released the FG model this year so I'm hoping some of the old FEs will go on clearance. Anyone know an online source or better yet a Canadian one that's clearing out old sustain reels? I'm hoping to get a bomb diggity reel for cheap.
The new Sustain is pretty nice we got them in last week at Gagnons. There set at $324.99 this year. We sold the couple old model Sustain's we had during the Christmas sale.
great, now I fell like I have to go for a drive...
